### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Decision query — RSI Oversold first slice (S43)
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Validates the decision domain vertical slice:
###   derive (RSI signal → RSI Oversold evaluator) → DECISION_EVENTS → store (projection) → gateway HTTP
###
### Prerequisites:
###   make up           # starts nats, configctl, gateway, ingest, derive, store
###   make seed         # seeds configctl with btcusdt binding
###   wait ~20min       # RSI needs 15 finalized 60s candles for warm-up;
###                     # decision evaluates immediately after each signal
###
### Note: Decision evaluates after every RSI signal. The first decision
### appears at the same time as the first RSI signal (~15 minutes).

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### 1. Latest RSI Oversold decision — btcusdt 60s
### Expected: 200 with decision data (after warm-up) or 200 with null decision
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Latest RSI Oversold decision — btcusdt 300s
### Expected: 200 with decision data (after 15x300s = 75min warm-up) or null
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Unknown decision type — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/unknown/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Missing timeframe — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt
Accept: application/json

###

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Multi-symbol verification (S46)
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Prerequisites:
###   make seed-multi    # seeds configctl with btcusdt + ethusdt
###   wait ~20min        # RSI warm-up + decision evaluation

### 5. Latest RSI Oversold decision — ethusdt 60s
### Expected: 200 with decision data (after warm-up) or 200 with null
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Latest RSI Oversold decision — ethusdt 300s
### Expected: 200 with decision data (after 75min warm-up) or null
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Cross-symbol back-to-back comparison — btcusdt vs ethusdt 60s
### Execute #1 and #5 back-to-back; verify different symbol fields in response
GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/decision/rsi_oversold/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###
